  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2412200/extras/6506a9f2ff45ceebb989d324dbcde26d.avif?t=1769007205\" width=613 height=1017 /></span><br><br>In the bleak 1920s, luck abandons you, gripped by debt and entangled by the local gangster, Mr. Blackwood. Your path veers to the accursed seaside town of Innsmouth, where a hidden treasure is rumored to lie within Devil Reef.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2412200/extras/84caf1f42d63f1027014db454442ddf2.webp?t=1769007205\" width=40 height=13 /></span> <strong>Embark solo or with companions</strong> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2412200/extras/7cc8a70ad3a08512885847c3cd08f9d9.webp?t=1769007205\" width=40 height=13 /></span> <br>Ferry to Devil Reef alone or with friends — let the journey begin.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2412200/extras/23e84f5e62360ef937a349837d676e1c.poster.avif?t=1769007205\" width=616 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2412200/extras/23e84f5e62360ef937a349837d676e1c.webm?t=1769007205\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2412200/extras/23e84f5e62360ef937a349837d676e1c.mp4?t=1769007205\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2412200/extras/84caf1f42d63f1027014db454442ddf2.webp?t=1769007205\" width=40 height=13 /></span> <strong>Explore Devil Reef and its horrors</strong> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2412200/extras/7cc8a70ad3a08512885847c3cd08f9d9.webp?t=1769007205\" width=40 height=13 /></span><br>What is thought to be an effortless treasure hunt changes fast as you venture deeper, amassing gold. The once-promising labyrinth reveals its sinister nature. Corridors contort, and eldritch horrors multiply, presenting a daunting challenge. Are you strong enough to reach the mythic treasure at the bottom of Devil Reef?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2412200/extras/8d045986830a8982da34d8165bbcc72d.poster.avif?t=1769007205\" width=616 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2412200/extras/8d045986830a8982da34d8165bbcc72d.webm?t=1769007205\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2412200/extras/8d045986830a8982da34d8165bbcc72d.mp4?t=1769007205\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2412200/extras/84caf1f42d63f1027014db454442ddf2.webp?t=1769007205\" width=40 height=13 /></span> <strong>Unlock powerful weapons and upgrades</strong> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2412200/extras/7cc8a70ad3a08512885847c3cd08f9d9.webp?t=1769007205\" width=40 height=13 /></span> <br>Bolster your chances for survival with arcane scrolls and incantations. Unlock and enhance weapons to confront the impending otherworldly battle ahead. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2412200/extras/1c70006d118320edcca9f0040346855c.poster.avif?t=1769007205\" width=616 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2412200/extras/1c70006d118320edcca9f0040346855c.webm?t=1769007205\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2412200/extras/1c70006d118320edcca9f0040346855c.mp4?t=1769007205\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2412200/extras/84caf1f42d63f1027014db454442ddf2.webp?t=1769007205\" width=40 height=13 /></span> <strong>Key features</strong> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2412200/extras/7cc8a70ad3a08512885847c3cd08f9d9.webp?t=1769007205\" width=40 height=13 /></span> <br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Isometric action roguelike gameplay <br></li><li>Up to 4 player online co-op multiplayer<br></li><li>Unlock weapons and upgrades to progress further<br></li><li>Atmospheric soundtrack and effects<br></li><li>Wide range of Incantations boosts and give you new abilities<br></li><li>Generative dungeons - Three Acts with unique bosses will be added during early access<br></li><li>Map Editor for custom player created maps - Will be added during early access</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2412200/extras/84caf1f42d63f1027014db454442ddf2.webp?t=1769007205\" width=40 height=13 /></span> <strong>Plunge Into the Abyss!</strong> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2412200/extras/7cc8a70ad3a08512885847c3cd08f9d9.webp?t=1769007205\" width=40 height=13 /></span> <br>Prepare for a chilling journey into the heart of darkness with Devil Reef, an action-packed roguelike co-op dungeon crawler developed by The Fine Arc Nordic AB. Immerse yourself in a haunting universe inspired by H.P. Lovecraft's twisted tales, where pixel-art graphics and atmospheric soundscapes pay homage to the golden era of 90s gaming - <strong><i>Wishlist now!</i></strong><br><br>Join the discussion on the Steam Forums or dive into the abyss on our Discord Server (link available in the side panel).<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2412200/extras/4e4ac158fb98cee1866a56cf0702f4f0.avif?t=1769007205\" width=616 height=300 /></span>",
